at%20his%20rank%2C%20Ruiz%20still%20takes%20the%20Marine%20Corps'%20two%20annual%20fitness%20tests%2C%20which%20measure%20both%20strength%20and%20endurance.%20The%20first%2C%20held%20in%20the%20year's%20opening%20half%2C%20includes%20a%20three-mile%20run%20%E2%80%94%20his%20fastest%20time%20is%20about%2016%3A30%2C%20or%20a%205%3A30-per-mile%20pace%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20pull-ups%20and%20a%20nearly%20four-minute%20plank.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20pull-up%20scores%20for%20men%20and%20women%20are%20usually%20just%20over%2020%20and%2010%20dead-hang%20pull-ups%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20annual%20test%2C%20held%20later%20in%20the%20year%2C%20simulates%20battlefield%20fitness%2C%20with%2030-pound%20%26quot%3Bammo%20can%26quot%3B%20presses%2C%20an%20800-meter%20sprint%2C%20and%20a%20timed%20agility%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuiz's%20wife%2C%20a%20retired%20Marine%2C%20puts%20him%20through%20his%20paces%20to%20keep%20his%20pull-ups%20and%20ammo-can%20lifts%20on%20point.%20As%20soon%20as%20he%20comes%20home%20after%20a%20long%20work%20day%2C%20he%20owes%20her%20a%20set%20of%20either%2C%20depending%20on%20which%20fitness%20test%20is%20around%20the%20corner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20holds%20me%20accountable%20at%20home%20because%20she's%20a%20Marine%20of%2022%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20it's%20over%20with%20the%20Marine%20Corps%2C%20I%20want%20to%20have%20another%20career.%20I'm%20not%20looking%20to%20retire%20out%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20explaining%20he's%20not%20one%20to%20sit%20still%20at%20home.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20to%20be%20functional.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237ec58a1-bab8-4e4a-a397-ea187050f7b1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERunning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERuiz%20is%20a%20religious%20runner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20days%20he%20runs%20a%20breezy%20five%20miles.%20On%20Sundays%2C%20when%20he's%20home%2C%20he%20goes%20for%20a%20ten-mile%20run%20from%20his%20home%20at%20the%20Corps'%20famous%208th%20and%20I%20barracks%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20weaving%20across%20the%20National%20Mall%2C%20and%20over%20to%20the%20Corps'%20Iwo%20Jima%20Memorial.%20Sometimes%20he%20spies%20Marine%20groups%20on%20the%20National%20Mall%20working%20out%20and%20pops%20by%20to%20say%20hello.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20warm-ups%2C%20a%20brisk%20walk%20and%20some%20stretching%2C%20are%20lengthier%20these%20days%20and%20an%20important%20part%20of%20his%20routine%20that%20he%20says%20helps%20to%20get%20his%20mind%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20me%20a%20long%20time%20to%20warm%20up.%20I%20love%20the%20process%20of%20getting%20ready%20for%20a%20run%2C%20being%20alone%20in%20my%20head.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERunning%20hasn't%20always%20come%20naturally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20took%20time%20for%20him%20to%20develop%20a%20deep%20love%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBad%20initial%20experiences%20can%20lead%20many%20to%20dislike%20running%2C%20Ruiz%20lamented%20%E2%80%94%20many%20are%20thrust%20into%20the%20service%20with%20little%20prior%20running%20experience%20and%20are%20forced%20into%20mass-unit%20runs%20with%20scores%20of%20other%20people%20wearing%20the%20wrong%20shoes%2C%20with%20no%20coaching%20for%20form%20or%20breathing%2C%20and%20poor%20diets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ruiz%20and%20other%20Marines%20did%20a%20round%20of%20push-ups%20after%20a%20unit%20run%20in%20Japan%20on%20Sep.%203%2C%202025%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6924d5a6e1a9cbb014dee1bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERuiz%20and%20other%20Marines%20did%20a%20round%20of%20push-ups%20after%20a%20unit%20run%20in%20Japan%20on%20Sep.%203%2C%202025%3Cp%3ECpl.%20Jeremiah%20Barksdale%2FUS%20Marine%20Corps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20can%20easily%20morph%20into%20a%20short%20survival%20test%20for%20many%20and%20end%20there%2C%20he%20said.%20It%20took%20years%20for%20his%20own%20love%20of%20running%20to%20develop.%20It%20is%20now%20a%20sacred%20part%20of%20his%20daily%20routine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20looking%20to%20get%20into%20running%20%E2%80%94%20and%20who%20can%20afford%20new%20shoes%20%E2%80%94%20Ruiz%20recommends%20getting%20fitted%20for%20the%20right%20pair%20to%20maximize%20comfort%20and%20prevent%20injuries.%20Make%20running%20enjoyable%2C%20he%20said%2C%20and%20give%20it%20time.%20It%20might%20take%20a%20few%20months%20before%20you%20start%20to%20appreciate%20the%20routine%20that's%20become%20therapeutic%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20anyone%20in%20need%20of%20maximum%20Marine%20Corps%20motivation%2C%20Ruiz%20recommended%20his%20current%20running%20playlist%20of%20Marine%20and%20Army%20cadence%2C%20the%20songs%20troops%20call%20out%20for%20marching%20(%26quot%3Bdouble%20time%26quot%3B%20tempo%20can%20equate%20to%20that%20of%20a%20leisurely%20jog).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6f22af8-d679-43d0-8dba-fc732120b13f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ERecovery%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20recovery%2C%20Ruiz%20sticks%20to%20the%20basics%20%E2%80%94%20good%20food%2C%20hydration%2C%20and%20rest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20knows%20he'll%20be%20sluggish%20on%20his%20daily%20run%20if%20he%20hasn't%20gotten%20enough%20water%20or%20electrolytes%2C%20or%20if%20he's%20out%20of%20balance%20with%20his%20carbohydrate%20intake.%20An%20out-of-whack%20diet%20for%20Ruiz%20means%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20going%20to%20be%20a%20quality%20and%20a%20comfortable%20run.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%2C%20it'll%20be%20one%20%26quot%3Bwhere%20I%20spend%20time%20struggling%20to%20get%20a%20rhythm%2C%20and%20not%20relaxing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERuiz%20is%20not%20one%20for%20trendy%20fitness%20bells%20and%20whistles%20except%20for%20one%20area%20%E2%80%94%20tracking%20his%20physical%20data%20like%20sleep%2C%20heart%20rate%2C%20and%20run%20times%20with%20a%20Garmin%20smart%20watch.%20It's%20