0rising%20from%20an%20associate%20during%20the%20Financial%20Crisis%20to%20a%20senior%20position%20overseeing%20the%20bank's%20%2420%20billion%20lending%20business%20with%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20commercial%20real%20estate%20landlords%20and%20developers.%20Business%20Insider%20featured%20Tredway%20in%20its%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbusiness-insider-rising-stars-under-35-asset-management-2017-10%23chad-tredway-34-jp-morgan-chase-52%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERising%20Stars%20of%20Wall%20Street%20list%20in%202017%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20in%202021%2C%20he%20left%20to%20launch%20his%20own%20real%20state%20company%2C%20called%20Trio%20Investment%20Group.%20The%20company%20focused%20on%20sale-leaseback%20transactions%20where%20it%20purchased%20property%20assets%20from%20owners%20who%20occupied%20their%20spaces%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20manufacturers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20leased%20it%20back%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJPMorgan%20brought%20him%20back%20by%20buying%20Tredway's%20firm%20in%20early%202024%20for%20an%20undisclosed%20price%20and%20named%20him%20head%20of%20real%20estate%20investment%20in%20the%20Americas%20for%20JPMorgan%20Asset%20Management%2C%20an%20investment%20arm%20of%20the%20bank%20that%20owns%20about%20%2479%20billion%20of%20commercial%20property.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%202025%2C%20Tredway%2C%2042%2C%20was%20promoted%20to%20global%20leader%20of%20that%20real%20estate%20investment%20business.%20In%20the%20new%20position%2C%20he%20regularly%20travels%20to%20meet%20with%20both%20existing%20and%20prospective%20clients%2C%20including%20some%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20caught%20up%20with%20Tredway%20on%20his%20career%20changes%20and%20the%20opportunities%20he%20sees%20in%20the%20real%20estate%20market%20amid%20a%20changing%20economy.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou