n%20the%20detail%20and%20the%20focus%20and%20what%20it%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchad-tredway-jpmorgan-real-estate-property-portfolio-2025-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1764418820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69275100abd5e944effb9768%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchad-tredway-jpmorgan-real-estate-property-portfolio-2025-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tredway%20had%20left%20JPMorgan%20to%20launch%20his%20own%20investment%20firm.%20Now%20he's%20back%20to%20capitalize%20on%20an%20ascendant%20real%20estate%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dgeiger%40businessinsider.com%20(Daniel%20Geiger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A28%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchad-tredway-jpmorgan-real-estate-property-portfolio-2025-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20get%20paid%20to%20wait%20in%20line%20for%20everything%20from%20sample%20sales%20to%20celebrity%20trials.%20I've%20learned%20there%20are%202%20key%20things%20people%20will%20pay%20for.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Gigi%20Principe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F691cb24be1a9cbb014de6eb4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPrincipe%20became%20a%20line-sitter%20in%202023.%3Cp%3EGigi%20Principe%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGigi%20Principe%2C%2026%2C%20became%20a%20line-sitter%20in%202023%20when%20her%20life%20was%20at%20a%20low%20point%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20waited%20in%20lines%20for%20access%20to%20restaurants%20%2C%20sample%20sales%2C%20and%20trials%20for%20lawyers%2C%20the%20press%2C%20and%20the%20public.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPrincipe%20said%20she%20has%20learned%20there%20are%20two%20key%20things%20people%20will%20pay%20for.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Gigi%20Principe%2C%2026%2C%20who%20has%20been%20working%20for%20Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%2C%20a%20line-sitting%20company%2C%20since%202023%20and%20is%20now%20a%20manager.%20Business%20Insider%20has%20verified%20her%20employment.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELife%20after%20graduating%20college%20in%202019%20meant%20bouncing%20from%20job%20to%20job%2C%20burning%20myself%20out%20at%20each%20one.%20Getting%20furloughed%20during%20the%20pandemic%20didn't%20help%2C%20but%20I%20eventually%20started%20working%20odd%20gigs%20again%20and%20auditioning%20for%20acting%20roles.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20I%20would%20struggle%20financially%2C%20then%20do%20okay%2C%20then%20struggle%2C%20then%20do%20okay.%20It%20was%20a%20pattern%20that%20I%20hated%2C%20but%20a%20pattern%20I%20was%20used%20to.%20It%20was%20so%20stressful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220242ecdc-e06f-48f2-a8d8-fb679aedfb9a%5C%22%3EThe%20job%20came%20at%20the%20right%20time%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20at%20my%20lowest%20year%20personally%2C%20a%20friend%20referred%20me%20to%20Same%20Ole%20Line%20Dudes%2C%20a%20company%20that%20pays%20people%20to%20wait%20in%20lines%20on%20their%20behalf.%20My%20first%20gig%20was%20a%20Jimmy%20Choo%20sample%20sale%20in%20October%20of%202023.%20When%20I%20first%20got%20the%20Google%20Invite%20form%20for%20the%20job%2C%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20a%20scam.%20All%20I%20had%20to%20do%20was%20show%20up%20and%20sit%20in%20line%2C%20and%20I'd%20get%20paid%20around%20%2474.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20only%20planning%20to%20be%20there%20for%20four%20hours%2C%20but%20I%20relooped%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20line%20for%20another%20client%20and%20made%20extra%20money.%20I%20basically%20got%20addicted%2C%20and%20soon%2C%20I%20was%20hustling.%20Once%20the%20compan